{"prompt": "Generate a website for a restaurant chain. The website should be elegant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elegance Eatery</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2c3e50; /* Dark Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #bdc3c7; /* Light Gray */\n            --accent-color: #34495e; /* Slightly lighter dark blue */\n            --text-color: #ecf0f1; /* Light Gray for text */\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff; /* White for headings */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section p {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin: 15px 20px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;\n            width: 250px;\n            vertical-align: top;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .menu-item h3 {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Elegance Eatery</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#menu\">Our Menu</a>\n        <a href=\"#locations\">Locations</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Experience Sophistication</h2>\n            <p>\n                Elegance Eatery is more than just a meal; it's an experience. We blend classic culinary artistry with contemporary flair to create dishes that delight the senses. Our commitment to quality ingredients and impeccable service ensures every visit is a memorable occasion.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"menu\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Signature Dishes</h2>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Pan-Seared Scallops</h3>\n                <p>Jumbo scallops seared to perfection, served with a lemon-butter reduction and asparagus risotto.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Truffle Mushroom Risotto</h3>\n                <p>Creamy Arborio rice infused with earthy truffle oil and a medley of wild mushrooms.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Filet Mignon</h3>\n                <p>Tender 8oz filet mignon, grilled to your preference, with a red wine glaze and garlic mashed potatoes.</p>\n            </div>\n             <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Lavender Cr\u00e8me Br\u00fbl\u00e9e</h3>\n                <p>A delicate custard infused with floral lavender, topped with a caramelized sugar crust.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"locations\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Find Us</h2>\n            <p>\n                Visit one of our elegantly appointed locations. We are proud to serve you in:\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <strong>New York City</strong> | <strong>Los Angeles</strong> | <strong>Chicago</strong> | <strong>Miami</strong>\n            </p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Elegance Eatery. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}